{"type": "article", "id": 22253, "title": "nendo带标签的笔记本", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-15T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125714p5f86uxyFdltOWVB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">nendo 推出的这款软面抄在边缘处自带标签，每一页都有 5 个可翻折的“L”型缺口，可以折出书页外变成小的标签卡，替代了贴标签纸的方式。软面抄采用磨砂线装订，内页是空白的，非常简洁，也有更多自由做笔记的空间。实际上，你也可以自己切割出标签条，但固定好位置的标签会显得更加整齐。这款软面抄是为瑞典设计公司 Claesson Koivisto Rune 的“smaller objects”项目设计，不久后将量产，<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/tab-note/?erelease\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125712jJIk12YxbZeSWnMc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257123Mt1GDaNEeCiv0oj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125713Dz2LrfSKGHo9xvst.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125713M0pPYzx9rgWNy6EK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}